    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <header class="hero">
        <div class="overlay"></div>
        <div class="container">
            <h1>Process Engineering</h1>
            <p>Master the art of designing and optimizing processes that transform raw materials into valuable products</p>
        </div>
    </header>

    <!-- About Section -->
    <section class="section" id="about">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title">What is Process Engineering?</h2>
            <div class="content-wrapper">
                <div class="text-content">
                    <p>Process Engineering is a core specialization within Chemical Engineering that focuses on the design, operation, control, and optimization of chemical, physical, and biological processes. It involves creating efficient systems to transform raw materials into valuable products, such as fuels, pharmaceuticals, food, and advanced materials.</p>
                    <p>As a process engineer, you'll develop and refine processes used in industries like petrochemicals, pharmaceuticals, food processing, and energy production. You'll apply principles of chemistry, physics, and mathematics to ensure processes are safe, sustainable, and cost-effective, addressing global challenges like energy efficiency and environmental impact.</p>
                    <p>With the rise of sustainable technologies and green chemistry, process engineers are in high demand to innovate and improve industrial processes, making this a dynamic and impactful career path.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="image-content">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1581091226825-a6a2a5aee158?ixlib=rb-1.2.1&auto=format&fit=crop&w=1350&q=80" alt="Process Engineering">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Key Areas Section -->
    <section class="section bg-dark" id="key-areas">
        <div class="container">
            <h2 class="section-title">Key Areas of Study</h2>
            <p class="section-intro">Process Engineering encompasses critical areas that form the backbone of industrial production and innovation:</p>
            
            <div class="cards-grid three-columns">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <h3><i class="fas fa-cogs"></i> Process Design</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-content">
                        <p>Creating and optimizing process flow diagrams, equipment layouts, and piping and instrumentation diagrams (P&IDs) for industrial plants.</p>
                        <ul class="skills-list">
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Flow Diagrams</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">PFDs, P&IDs, process schematics</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Equipment Sizing</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Reactors, heat exchangers, pumps</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Process Simulation</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">ASPEN Plus, HYSYS, ChemCAD</p>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <h3><i class="fas fa-thermometer"></i> Thermodynamics</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-content">
                        <p>Applying thermodynamic principles to analyze energy balances, phase equilibria, and heat transfer in chemical processes.</p>
                        <ul class="skills-list">
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Energy Balances</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Heat, work, and energy flow calculations</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Phase Equilibria</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Vapor-liquid, liquid-liquid systems</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Heat Transfer</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Conduction, convection, radiation</p>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <h3><i class="fas fa-tint"></i> Fluid Mechanics</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-content">
                        <p>Understanding fluid flow, pressure drops, and transport phenomena to design pipelines, pumps, and fluid systems.</p>
                        <ul class="skills-list">
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Fluid Flow</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Laminar, turbulent flow, Bernoulli's principle</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Pump Design</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Centrifugal, positive displacement pumps</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Pipeline Systems</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Pressure drop, pipe sizing</p>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="cards-grid three-columns" style="margin-top: 1.5rem;">
                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <h3><i class="fas fa-flask"></i> Reaction Engineering</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-content">
                        <p>Designing and optimizing chemical reactors to maximize yield, efficiency, and safety in chemical transformations.</p>
                        <ul class="skills-list">
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Kinetics</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Reaction rates, rate laws</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Reactor Design</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">CSTR, PFR, batch reactors</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Catalysis</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Catalyst selection, reaction enhancement</p>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <h3><i class="fas fa-exchange-alt"></i> Mass Transfer</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-content">
                        <p>Studying mass transfer operations like distillation, absorption, and extraction to separate and purify products.</p>
                        <ul class="skills-list">
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Distillation</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Vapor-liquid separation, column design</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Absorption</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Gas-liquid interactions, scrubbers</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Extraction</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Liquid-liquid separation, solvent selection</p>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="card">
                    <div class="card-header">
                        <h3><i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i> Process Safety</h3>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card-content">
                        <p>Ensuring processes are safe through risk assessment, hazard analysis, and adherence to safety standards.</p>
                        <ul class="skills-list">
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">HAZOP Analysis</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Hazard and operability studies</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Risk Assessment</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">Quantitative and qualitative risk analysis</p>
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <span class="skill-name">Safety Standards</span>
                                <p class="skill-desc">OSHA, ISO 45001 compliance</p>
                            </li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

